<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="71" type="type locality">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Type locality.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Iran, Alborz Mountains, Damavand, 2000 m.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="71" type="notes on type locality">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Notes on type locality.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="71">The locality is situated in the Province of Tehran, in the Damavand County (Central Alborz Range). Data on the label are insufficient to locate whether the holotype has been collected in the surrounding area of the Damavand City or in foothills of the Mount Damavand.</paragraph>
